Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.14,0:01:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後然後  五班有個超可愛的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.16,0:01:39.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女生有那麼一點點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.80,0:01:41.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏目  你有在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.04,0:01:42.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.44,0:01:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我在聽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.17,0:01:49.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她那雙清澈的眼睛直直的看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.56,0:01:50.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什麼名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.81,0:01:54.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字不知道  因為她一句話都不說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎——
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.50,0:01:59.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪裡  夏目？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:00.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.41,0:02:02.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說五班有個可愛女生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.30,0:02:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.70,0:02:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  趕快走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.88,0:02:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.11,0:02:08.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼夏目也要去？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.18,0:02:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走快點走快點  休息時間要結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.47,0:02:13.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.33,0:02:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…啊  有了有了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.52,0:02:21.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.47,0:02:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是她  是她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.70,0:02:34.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  很可愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.04,0:02:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  感覺好像有點陰沉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.00,0:02:39.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是看點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.20,0:02:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  站起來了  要出來囉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.17,0:02:46.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.09,0:02:51.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是二班的西村
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:55.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想跟你做個朋友啊…之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.19,0:03:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.78,0:03:10.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  她的確是看著我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.13,0:03:12.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有嗎  你多心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.81,0:03:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
